Name: Blue-Eyes White Dragon
Description: A legendary dragon that takes pride in its enormous power. Its powers of destruction far exceed comprehension.

Name: Mystical Elf
Description: An elf with blue skin, yellow hair, and light of element. It can power up Blue-Eyes White Dragons on the own field.

Name: Hitotsu-Me Giant
Description: A one-eyed giant that pummels foes with its thick arms. It must be treated with wary respect.

Name: Baby Dragon
Description: Despite its infancy, this dragon must not be taken lightly. The power it embodies is unimaginable.

Name: Ryu-Kishin
Description: It disguises itself as a statue and strikes from the shadows. It is also fleet of foot and adept at fleeing.

Name: Feral Imp
Description: A small but fierce fiend known for its mischievous ways. Beware - it uses the cover of darkness to attack the unwary.

Name: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #1
Description: A winged dragon that stands guard at a mountain fortress. It attacks by plummeting down from the sky in a steep dive.

Name: Mushroom Man
Description: A monster that is at its best in chilly and damp locations. It attacks by releasing clouds of spores from its cap.

Name: Shadow Specter
Description: A ghostly spirit of a wild animal that roams in wastelands. This card could become troublesome if encountered in number.

Name: Blackland Fire Dragon
Description: A dragon that makes its lair deep in impenetrable darkness. Its power of vision is not very good.

Name: Sword Arm of Dragon
Description: A dinosaur that bristles with swordlike spikes all over. It attacks by recklessly ramming its foe.

Name: Swamp Battleguard
Description: A loutish, troll-like warrior with thick muscles and build. It powers up Lava Battleguards on the player's own field.

Name: Tyhone
Description: Fires cannon shells over long distances from its mouth to attack. The power of its cannon is enhanced in mountainous terrain.

Name: Battle Steer
Description: A forest-dwelling fiend that is part man and part ox. It attacks by lowering its head and ramming with its horn.

Name: Flame Swordsman
Description: A swordsman that bears a fiery sword deadly to all dinosaurs. It has the power to wipe out all dinosaurs on the foe's field.

Name: Time Wizard
Description: An enchanted clock that has the power to transform Baby Dragons and Dark Magicians on the player's own field.

Name: Right Leg of the Forbidden One
Description: One of the five limbs of Exodia, the forbidden monster. If all five cards gather in the hand of the player, he wins.

Name: Left Leg of the Forbidden One
Description: One of the five limbs of Exodia, the forbidden monster. If all five cards gather in the hand of the player, he wins.

Name: Right Arm of the Forbidden One
Description: One of the five limbs of Exodia, the forbidden monster. If all five cards gather in the hand of the player, he wins.

Name: Left Arm of the Forbidden One
Description: One of the five limbs of Exodia, the forbidden monster. If all five cards gather in the hand of the player, he wins.

Name: Exodia the Forbidden One
Description: One of the five limbs of Exodia, the forbidden monster. If all five cards gather in the hand of the player, he wins.

Name: Summoned Skull
Description: A skeletal fiend that fools people with the power of darkness. It is among the stronger of the fiend types.

Name: The Wicked Worm Beast
Description: An earthworm that became a monster from the power of darkness. It burrows underground and attacks suddenly without warning.

Name: Skull Servant
Description: A skeletal specter that can appear virtually anywhere. Though its power is weak, it can be a threat in a swarm.

Name: Horn Imp
Description: A small fiend that dwells among shadows and darkness. Despite its stature, it is surprisingly strong. Beware of its horn.

Name: Battle Ox
Description: A fearsome ox monster that wields the power of Axe Crusher. When used, it eliminates all pyro types from the enemy field.

Name: Beaver Warrior
Description: A small and furry warrior that is fully armored and armed. Though it is small, it has high defense in grasslands.

Name: Rock Ogre Grotto #1
Description: With a body made of stone, it is strongly protected from damage. Beware - it swings its thick arms to devastating effect.

Name: Mountain Warrior
Description: A muscular warrior built to withstand harsh elements and terrain. It has no trouble getting about on even terrible ground.

Name: Zombie Warrior
Description: A skeletal warrior that is equipped with a sword and shield. It appears weak, but it strikes with quick, sharp stabs.

Name: Koumori Dragon
Description: A vicious, batlike dragon with wings, long tail, and sharp teeth. It spews a black and fiery breath that turns souls dark.

Name: Two-Headed King Rex
Description: A two-headed dinosaur that can attack in two directions at once. It is among the stronger of the dinosaur cards.

Name: Judge Man
Description: A warrior that detests battles without a clear outcome. A blow from its huge club is extremely powerful.

Name: Saggi the Dark Clown
Description: A sinister clown that appears as if from nowhere silently. It deftly evades attacks using strange motions.

Name: Dark Magician
Description: A sinister spell caster that possesses both power and defense. It is among the best of all magicians.

Name: The Snake Hair
Description: A dangerous female monster with the head of a venomous snake. Anyone that sees her eyes is instantly turned into stone.

Name: Gaia the Dragon Champion
Description: A powerful knight that sits astride its dragon steer. The knight's power and the dragon's speed combine for best effect.

Name: Gaia The Fierce Knight
Description: A powerful knight that rides a horse faster than the wind. Beware of its charging attack.

Name: Curse of Dragon
Description: A yellow dragon that breathes the very flames of hell. Its fiery breath can turn the field into a wasteland.

Name: Dragon Piper
Description: A being that dwells inside a curiously decorated vase. Its defense rating is very high.

Name: Celtic Guardian
Description: An elf that has been given training in the ways of the sword. It befuddles the foe with its lightning-quick attacks.

Name: Illusionist Faceless Mage
Description: An odd being without a face but with heads on both its shoulders. It can stop all enemies on the field from moving the next turn.

Name: Karbonala Warrior
Description: A deceptive card of what appears to be an ordinary swordsman. However, it has a notably high attack power.

Name: Rogue Doll
Description: A possessed doll that wields sacred power as its weapon. Its attacks become more powerful in darkness.

Name: Oscillo Hero #2
Description: A small but tough robot with a strong thunderbolt attack. Treating it lightly could come as a nasty shock.

Name: Griffore
Description: A hulking beast that is well protected by its hard body. Weak attacks simply bounce right off its rugged hide.

Name: Torike
Description: A smaller creature that is much more fragile than it appears. However, its long horns make its ramming charges powerful.

Name: Sangan
Description: A smaller fiend with a set of three malevolent eyes. It becomes more powerful in darkness.

Name: Big Insect
Description: A gigantic ant that makes its home in deep forests and jungles. Its attack and defense stats are surprisingly high.

Name: Basic Insect
Description: An insect with oversized front legs that lives in a swarm. Forests are paradise to them.

Name: Armored Lizard
Description: As its name implies, this lizard is clad in an armorlike hide. A bite of its cavernous mouth can be deadly.

Name: Hercules Beetle
Description: A gigantic stag beetle with imposing horns and a hard shell. Its horn attack and rugged defense make it very tough.

Name: Killer Needle
Description: An enormous bee that has more strength than it first appears. It can be a serious threat if it were to swarm with others.

Name: Gokibore
Description: A cockroach that curls up into a ball and rolls to attack. Its defense rating is much higher than it first appears.

Name: Giant Flea
Description: An enormous, blood-sucking flea that is surprisingly strong. Don't let the fact of it being a flea fool you into complacency.

Name: Larvae Moth
Description: Because it is only an undeveloped larva, it is very weak. However, it grows into an enormous moth.

Name: Great Moth
Description: A huge moth that attacks by scattering flurries of toxic dust. It is quite powerful when encountered in a forest.

Name: Kuriboh
Description: A small and furry fiend that is not much of a threat. However, it can be a pain if they appear in numbers in darkness.

Name: Mammoth Graveyard
Description: An animated skeleton of a mammoth with a debilitating power. It can power down every monster on the enemy's field.

Name: Great White
Description: An enormous great white shark of fearsome ferocity and speed. There is no escape if it were to clamp down with its huge jaws.

Name: Wolf
Description: A predatory beast that has become rarely seen in recent times. It searches for prey using its excellent sense of smell.

Name: Harpie Lady
Description: A female monster that is half bird and half human. It can power up Harpie's Pet Dragons on the own field.

Name: Harpie Lady Sisters
Description: A trio of Harpie Ladies, sisters half bird and half human. It can power up Harpie's Pet Dragons on the own field two levels.

Name: Tiger Axe
Description: A tigerlike beast warrior that is armed with a hefty axe. It doles out powerful blows with lightning quickness.

Name: Silver Fang
Description: A strikingly gorgeous wolf that glows in a whitish silver. Despite its beautiful look, it is extremely vicious.

Name: Kojikocy
Description: A thoroughly evil hunter that considers humans fair game. Its brute strength lets it crush rocks into shards.

Name: Perfectly Ultimate Great Moth
Description: The final evolution of the insect monster Great Moth. It is the most powerful among all the insect type monsters.

Name: Garoozis
Description: A ferocious beast warrior that has the head of a dragon. Its axe attacks have the power to inflict severe damage.

Name: Thousand Dragon
Description: A dragon that has lived for thousands and thousands of years. It breathes laboriously through its nostrils.

Name: Fiend Kraken
Description: An enormous squid that hides itself beneath ocean waves. It appears from the sea suddenly and attacks.

Name: Jellyfish
Description: A jellyfish that drifts aimlessly on the sea among waves. Its body is translucent, making it hard to distinguish its shape.

Name: Cocoon of Evolution
Description: An insect cocoon that is incapable of mounting an attack. It can take in an insect larva and make it evolve into maturity.

Name: Kairyu-Shin
Description: A gigantic sea dragon that creates massive tidal waves. It has the power to turn the field into a sea.

Name: Giant Soldier of Stone
Description: A massive warrior hewn from boulders that rattles the earth. It has the power to turn the field into an arena.

Name: Man-Eating Plant
Description: A thorny plant with what appears to be a lovely flower. However, the flower is used to swallow unsuspecting prey.

Name: Krokodilus
Description: A crocodile that became intelligent, but also more ferocious. It repels attacks with its hard and scaly hide.

Name: Grappler
Description: A sly and deceptive serpent with a long, thick body. Beware of its powerful constrictor attack.

Name: Axe Raider
Description: A wild and primitive warrior that arms itself with an axe. It metes out powerful blows by swinging its axe in one hand.

Name: Megazowler
Description: A dinosaur with horns protruding from all over its body. As expected, its ramming attacks are very powerful.

Name: Uraby
Description: A dinosaur that is adept at running at a very rapid pace. It attacks with hooked, razor-sharp claws.

Name: Crawling Dragon #2
Description: A ghoulish dinosaur with a mouth that pulverizes all it eats. Its attack power is quite high.

Name: Red-Eyes B. Dragon
Description: A sinister black dragon with eyes that shine a deep scarlet. It furiously spouts black flames that incinerate all things.

Name: Castle of Dark Illusions
Description: A macabre flying castle that can turn the field into darkness. It can also turn all own monsters in the field face down.

Name: Reaper of the Cards
Description: A deathly phantom in a cloaked hood with a giant blade. It can make one trap card disappear from the opponent's field.

Name: King of Yamimakai
Description: A wickedly cruel being that bears an awful power of darkness. It destroys all around it with its overwhelming power.

Name: Barox
Description: A winged creature that flies about freely in full darkness. It punches foes with its long and hairy arms.

Name: Dark Chimera
Description: A powerful monster that dwells in the dark world of fiends. It attacks by breathing the fires of darkness.

Name: Metal Guardian
Description: A fiend that guards the treasures in the world of fiends. Its defense in darkness is outstandingly high.

Name: Catapult Turtle
Description: A monster that can make all the unused monsters on the player's field disappear and hit the foe with their combined power.

Name: Gyakutenno Megami
Description: A goddess that can alter the course of battle. It can power up all monsters on the own field with attack of 500 or less.

Name: Mystic Horseman
Description: An axe-bearing beast that is half human and half horse. Fleet of foot, it is impossible for anyone to catch.

Name: Rabid Horseman
Description: A fearsome monster that is made of a centaur and an ox. It savagely doles out very punishing attacks.

Name: Zanki
Description: An armored swordsman that prefers to duel head to head. It strikes with viperlike quickness if the foe is off guard.

Name: Crawling Dragon
Description: A dragon that grew weak and became incapable of flying. In spite of that, it still retains its power for attacking.

Name: Crass Clown
Description: A malevolent clown that dances in the circus of darkness. Those that see its dance loses energy and strength.

Name: Armored Zombie
Description: An armored warrior that returned from the dead with evil intent. It waves its sword wildly with seemingly no control.

Name: Dragon Zombie
Description: A dragon that has been resurrected by the power of darkness. It breathes a corrosive gas that rots everything it touches.

Name: Clown Zombie
Description: A clown that has been resurrected by the power of darkness. Its stumbly dancing draws its audience to death's embrace.

Name: Pumpking the King of Ghosts
Description: A ghostly pumpkin with the ability to power up the player's Armored Zombie, Dragon Zombie and Clown Zombie in play.

Name: Battle Warrior
Description: A proud and muscle-bound warrior that has no use for weapons. Instead, it chooses to battle using only its bare knuckles.

Name: Wings of Wicked Flame
Description: The wings of this creature shimmer with red-black flames. It attacks by making fire erupt from all over its body.

Name: Mask of Darkness
Description: An animated mask created by a magician using dark powers. It attacks using a dark power that cannot be seen.

Name: Job-Change Mirror
Description: A sinister mirror that was crafted at the hands of fiends. It absorbs attacks without shattering to provide protection.

Name: Curtain of the Dark Ones
Description: A possessed curtain made by magicians using special powers. It is said to enhance the power of magic users.

Name: Tomozaurus
Description: A small dinosaur that is utterly fearless and ferocious. It is known to squabble and fight with others.

Name: Spirit of the Winds
Description: A free-spirited wind elemental that flits about as it desires. It brings storms when it becomes upset.

Name: Kageningen
Description: A creepy being whose shadow joins it to attack its foes. The unwary are caught by surprise from the front and rear.

Name: Graveyard and the Hand of Invitation
Description: A malevolent graveyard that gives greater strength to the dead. It beckons the living to the realm of death.

Name: Goddess with the Third Eye
Description: A goddess that has a divine third eye on her forehead. The divine eye gives her all-seeing powers.

Name: Hero of the East
Description: A samurai said to have come from a far-off land in the east. The katana it bears is extremely sharp.

Name: Doma The Angel of Silence
Description: The angel of death, this being must never be angered. To earn its wrath is to know death.

Name: That Which Feeds on Life
Description: A voracious fiend that eats the souls of all living things. The souls it consumes become its energy.

Name: Dark Gray
Description: A goatlike creature with small wings and a dark gray hide. It is very precious and rarely seen.

Name: White Magical Hat
Description: A mystical thief with a dazzling white cape and top hat. Despite his eye-catching attire, he has never been caught.

Name: Kamionwizard
Description: A wizard that is versed in the dark magic spells of chaos. Its large, cruel scythe inflicts harsh damage.

Name: Nightmare Scorpion
Description: A scorpion that lulls its foes to sleep and terrible nightmares. The sleeping foe is then stabbed by its four toxic stingers.

Name: Spirit of the Books
Description: A small, robed bird that serves as the spirit of books. It can summon a Boo Koo to an open spot on the own field.

Name: Supporter in the Shadows
Description: An adorable, tiny person who is eager to please, but quietly. It is happy to provide support from the shadows.

Name: Trial of Nightmare
Description: An emissary of hell that traps its foe inside a large coffin. It then renders its judgment that skewers the coffin.

Name: Dream Clown
Description: A peculiar, small being that has taken the guise of a clown. Its sweet dancing lulls the viewer to an eternal sleep.

Name: Sleeping Lion
Description: An utterly ferocious beast that is usually fast asleep. It becomes uncontrollable upon waking.

Name: Yamatano Dragon Scroll
Description: A dragon that emerges from inside a wall scroll to attack. Its defense rating is on the very low side.

Name: Dark Plant
Description: A malignant flower grown in polluted soil with dark powers. It is extremely wild and vicious.

Name: Ancient Tool
Description: A machine that was found in the ruins of an ancient culture. It appears to have been made solely to destroy.

Name: Faith Bird
Description: A divine bird with extremely long, flowing tail feathers. It shines all over with a sacred light.

Name: Orion the Battle King
Description: An imposing angel that is claimed to be the god of battle. No one, however, has been witness to it in battle.

Name: Ansatsu
Description: A stealthy warrior that is a deadly assassination specialist. It cunningly sneaks up on targets without a sound in darkness.

Name: LaMoon
Description: A female spell caster, who makes her home on the moon. She allures foes with the magical powers of the moon.

Name: Nemuriko
Description: A sleeping child that is swaddled in an enchanted scarf. It can make all enemy monsters on the field fall asleep.

Name: Weather Control
Description: A whimsical being with the ability to control the weather. It can be blamed for the fickle climate changes on mountains.

Name: Octoberser
Description: A bizarre creature with a fish head and octopus tentacles. It attacks with a spear.

Name: The 13th Grave
Description: A shambling skeleton of a zombie risen from death's sleep. It came from a supposedly unfilled plot, the 13th in a cemetery.

Name: Charubin the Fire Knight
Description: A knight in an enchanted armor that guards against fire. Because of it, he is unharmed even in an inferno.

Name: Mystical Capture Chain
Description: A magical chain that has been infused with a sacred power. It is said to be able to bind foes and keep them from moving.

Name: Fiend's Hand
Description: A spectral hand of the undead that tugs and pulls at victims. It can drag an enemy monster from the field to die together.

Name: Witty Phantom
Description: A charming and dapper fiend that represents death. Its attire is a jet-black tuxedo that melts into shadows.

Name: Mystery Hand
Description: The hand of a being that has the power to distort the dimensions. It reaches from a rift in the dimensions to strike.

Name: Dragon Statue
Description: A stone statue of a warrior with the soul of a dragon. It cleaves foes with its prized sword.

Name: Blue-Eyed Silver Zombie
Description: A horrifying being that fires a deadly ray from its one eye. The ray is said to turn victims into zombies.

Name: Toad Master
Description: A green-skinned figure that has the power to control frogs. It can summon a Frog the Jam to an open spot on the own field.

Name: Spiked Snail
Description: A malevolent snail that evolved using the power of darkness. It grew arms and legs that enable it to move quickly.

Name: Flame Manipulator
Description: A magician who is an expert at the manipulation of fire. He attacks by creating fiery pools and walls.

Name: Necrolancer the Timelord
Description: A one-eyed being that has the ability to bend time as it wants. It emerges from a ring of time that can appear anywhere.

Name: Djinn the Watcher of the Wind
Description: A magician that has full mastery over the powers of winds. It whips up tornadoes and gusts to blow away anything nearby.

Name: The Bewitching Phantom Thief
Description: A suave and debonair thief who swaddles himself in a black cape. He enchants enemies by exquisitely twirling his cane.

Name: Temple of Skulls
Description: An eerie temple made entirely of a skull and some bones. It draws in anyone unwary enough to get too close.

Name: Monster Egg
Description: An enigmatic warrior that hides itself inside a large egg shell. It attacks by flinging the shell at its foe.

Name: The Shadow Who Controls the Dark
Description: A malignant shadow that stealthily merges with darkness. It uses a paralyzing spell to stop foes from moving.

Name: Lord of the Lamp
Description: A rotund genie that emerges from an enchanted lamp. It obeys every command of whoever has summoned it.

Name: Akihiron
Description: A bizarre creature that hides itself in the safety of water. Its strange appearance is mind-boggling.

Name: Rhaimundos of the Red Sword
Description: A warrior armed with a sword that blazes with red flames. It uses a fiery skill that prevents the foe from moving.

Name: The Melting Red Shadow
Description: A peculiar being that can make its body dissolve into a fluid. It then sneaks under the foe and strikes from beneath.

Name: Dokuroizo the Grim Reaper
Description: A menacing grim reaper that wears a red hooded cloak. It tries to take the souls of foes with hellish scythe slashes.

Name: Fire Reaper
Description: A skeletal grim reaper that is armed with fiery arrows. Its arrow can directly inflict 50LP damage on the opponent.

Name: Larvas
Description: A monstrous bird that moves with darting quickness. It binds and squeezes the foe with its long and thin arms.

Name: Hard Armor
Description: An empty yet animated suit of armor that has a living soul. It throws military-style tackles with its hard body.

Name: Firegrass
Description: A peculiar plant that grows in the wild near volcanoes. It attacks by blowing fire from its flowers.

Name: Man Eater
Description: A carnivorous plant that feasts on the flesh of humans. It attacks with its toxic tentacles.

Name: Dig Beak
Description: A reptilian beast with a long, snakelike body and a beak. It curls up into a ball to roll and hack with its large beak.

Name: M-Warrior #1
Description: A striking, blue-skinned warrior armed with a conical sword. It can power up M-Warrior #2s on the own field.

Name: M-Warrior #2
Description: A striking, red-skinned warrior armed with a flat blade. It can power up M-Warrior #1s on the own field.

Name: Tainted Wisdom
Description: A malignant brain that attacks foes with stabbing tentacles. It absorbs the brain cells of foes and makes them its own.

Name: Lisark
Description: A jarringly colored beast that has eyes composed of sapphires. It confuses its foe with miragelike visions, then strikes.

Name: Lord of Zemia
Description: A pagan deity in the form of a large winged creature. It tricks foes into following a path of self-destruction.

Name: The Judgement Hand
Description: A seemingly disembodied hand that is endowed with god's power. It renders final judgments and metes harsh punishment.

Name: Mysterious Puppeteer
Description: A horrifying puppeteer that has the power to mesmerize its foes. Once a foe is under this being's spell, it becomes a mere puppet.

Name: Ancient Jar
Description: An easily broken jar that was made in ancient times. Something appears to lurk within its murky confines.

Name: Darkfire Dragon
Description: A dragon that breathes the intense flames of the dark world. Its breath obliterates everything instantly.

Name: Dark King of the Abyss
Description: A powerful fiend that rules the dark world of the Abyss. It is said to have had the power to rule all that is darkness.

Name: Spirit of the Harp
Description: An angelic spirit that strums a harp high in the heavens. The gentle melodies it plays becalm souls.

Name: Big Eye
Description: A bizarre being that has eyes peering from all over its body. It uses the numerous eyes to hypnotize its foes.

Name: Armaill
Description: A remarkable warrior with a tail that is in the form of a sword. It launches 3-hit attacks with its two arms and its tail.

Name: Dark Prisoner
Description: A furtive, dark fiend that cleverly manipulates light. It uses the reflections of light to hide itself from sight.

Name: Hurricail
Description: A possessed tornado that rages out of control in wastelands. It tears at its foes with razor-sharp winds.

Name: Ancient Brain
Description: A fallen angel that has been banished from the heavens. It is highly skilled at the use of dark powers for fighting.

Name: Fire Eye
Description: A sinister eye with large wings that is engulfed in flames. It whips up fiery winds by flapping its wings.

Name: Monsturtle
Description: A massively armored turtle enclosed in a shell studded with spikes. Extremely aggressive, it will not grow obedient to people.

Name: Claw Reacher
Description: An armored fiend that can freely extend its arms as desired. It does so to skewer its foe with its sharply clawed hands.

Name: Phantom Dewan
Description: A macabre magician with the ability to cast dark spells. It can stop foes in their tracks using immobilizing curses.

Name: Arlownay
Description: A female being that lurks in a flower to cast toxic dust. She is very dangerous and must not be approached.

Name: Dark Shade
Description: A bizarre, round being ringed with six winglike appendages. It emits a powerful ray from a crystal to attack.

Name: Masked Clown
Description: A masked warrior that prances about in the dance of death. While it is dancing, it hacks at its foe with its scythe.

Name: Lucky Trinket
Description: A peculiar, grinning being with numerous tiny legs and wings. Although it appears to be frail, it is protected by a holy power.

Name: Genin
Description: A being that that uses its illusionary spells to beat foes. It also conjures doves to carry out its attacks.

Name: Eyearmor
Description: A one-eyed creature that has the power to transform into others. It keeps its foes offguard by changing its guise in battle.

Name: Fiend Reflection #2
Description: A bird that clutches an enchanted mirror in its talons. It summons other monsters through its mirror.

Name: Gate Deeg
Description: A sinister, orblike being with a door mounted on its belly. The door is one that leads straight to hell.

Name: Synchar
Description: A grotesque beast that has two heads, on top and down below. It shoots laser beams from its two mouths.

Name: Fusionist
Description: A feline monster that has angelic wings and a long tail. The pink, furry tail is much longer than its body.

Name: Akakieisu
Description: A clownlike magician that lays death curses on its opponents. Anyone that listens to its spell chants grows faint.

Name: LaLa Li-oon
Description: A cloudlike monster that is charged with powerful electricity. It unleashes downpours of a fluid that dissolves all substances.

Name: Key Mace
Description: A very small angel that is the picture of cuteness with its key. Its adorable qualities let it unlock the hearts of its foes.

Name: Turtle Tiger
Description: A ferocious tiger enclosed in a sturdy, tortoiselike shell. Protected by the durable shell, it attacks with sharp fangs.

Name: Terra the Terrible
Description: A swamp-dwelling fiend that calls another fiend its master. While it is not as strong as it looks, don't treat it lightly.

Name: Doron
Description: A striped warrior that can create a copy of itself in battle. It can do so if there is an empty spot on the player's field.

Name: Arma Knight
Description: A marine warrior that has assumed the guise of an ammonite. From ancient times, it has protected the sea from outsiders.

Name: Mech Mole Zombie
Description: An undead monster with the build of a mole and bony hands. It launches its skeletal hands like rockets to attack.

Name: Happy Lover
Description: A minuscule angel with wings in the place of legs for flight. It shoots a beam that induces euphoria from the heart on its head.

Name: Penguin Knight
Description: An imperious penguin that is armed with an imposing sword. It leaps and slides on its belly to make a charge at foes.

Name: Petit Dragon
Description: A very tiny dragon with wings that are as large as its body. It bravely attacks foes using its puny body to the fullest.

Name: Frenzied Panda
Description: A seemingly adorable beast that actually is extremely aggressive. It is always armed with a stout bamboo pole.

Name: Air Marmot of Nefariousness
Description: A ferocious marmot that has the horn and wings of a fiend. It attacks by hurling acorns.

Name: Phantom Ghost
Description: A macabre being that is actually a gathering of lost souls. The souls are those unable to pass on to the next world.

Name: Mabarrel
Description: A fiend with a long snout that works like a cannon. It shoots eyeballs at a speed that is invisible to the eye.

Name: Dorover
Description: A revolting monster that has a body made of horrid slime. It attacks by spewing horrible toxic gases.

Name: Twin Long Rods #1
Description: A small creature with a pair of slender, whiplike arms. Using its arms, it can lash foes from a distance.

Name: Droll Bird
Description: A curious bird that has a large, flat, and broad beak. It looses loud cries to startle timid foes.

Name: Petit Angel
Description: An extremely small angel that darts and dashes about quickly. Its small size and quick agility make it a difficult target.

Name: Winged Cleaver
Description: A menacing insect with a foreleg that evolved into a scythe. It swings the scythe arm wildly like a windmill to attack.

Name: Hinotama Soul
Description: A terrifying monster that is made up of intensely hot flames. It charges into foes with its furiously flaming body.

Name: Kaminarikozou
Description: A young monster that keeps lightning charged in its body. It can turn dangerous if anyone were to make it cry.

Name: Meotoko
Description: An enormous, headless beast with an eye glaring from its chest. It attacks by shooting a destructive beam from its eye.

Name: Aqua Madoor
Description: A masked magician with the power to manipulate water. It creates thick walls of water to crush foes.

Name: Kagemusha of the Blue Flame
Description: A dutiful warrior that serves as the double of its master. It is armed with a sword renowned for its sharpness.

Name: Flame Ghost
Description: A skeletal ghost of someone who was burned to death. The flames enshrouding its body can never be extinguished.

Name: Dryad
Description: An ethereal and devout elemental nymph of the forests. She prevents the foe from moving with the help of plants.

Name: B. Skull Dragon
Description: A fiendish dark dragon that is of extremely high rarity. It is the fusion of a rare fiend and a dragon.

Name: Two-Mouth Darkruler
Description: A horrible dinosaur that has two gaping mouths and a horn. Electricity is charged in the horn and released from the mouth.

Name: Solitude
Description: A centaurlike beast warrior with the body of a deer. It is armed with a scythe that is said to drain away souls.

Name: Masked Sorcerer
Description: A secretive sorcerer who conceals his identity with a mask. No one has ever seen the sorcerer's face.

Name: Kumootoko
Description: An enormous spider that grew not only cunning, but intelligent. It sprays silk from its mouth to hold foes immobile.

Name: Midnight Fiend
Description: A fiendish bird monster that appears only late at night. It is said to require a sacrifice for it to be summoned.

Name: Roaring Ocean Snake
Description: A gigantic sea serpent that emerges from the waves in a storm. It creates towering tidal waves that swallow all in their path.

Name: Trap Master
Description: A masked warrior who is an expert at setting deadly traps. He can set an Acid Trap Hole on an open spot on the own fiel

Name: Fiend Sword
Description: A powerful sword that is possessed by an ancient curse. It empowers anyone that can overcome its curse.

Name: Skull Stalker
Description: An agile scorpion warrior with a long, stinger-tipped tail. It traps its foe with pincers and stabs with the stinger.

Name: Hitodenchak
Description: A starfish that mutated into a monster from polluted water. It spews a corrosive solvent from its mouth.

Name: Wood Remains
Description: A spectral being that had once been the master of a forest. It has been resurrected at the hands of evil.

Name: Hourglass of Life
Description: An enchanted hourglass that can exchange strength for vitality. It can power up all monsters on the own field for 1000LP.

Name: Rare Fish
Description: A peculiar, rarely seen fish that has the head of a beast. Its temperament is very aggressive.

Name: Wood Clown
Description: A small, unpleasantly leering fiend in the form of a joker. It cleverly parries away attacks with its sickle.

Name: Madjinn Gunn
Description: A bio-weapon with seemingly three heads, but only two eyes. It shoots projectiles at high speed from its mouth.

Name: Dark Titan of Terror
Description: A fiend with many faces that is said to lurk in dreams. It steals lives while the victims sleep.

Name: Beautiful Headhuntress
Description: A ravishing beauty of a Japanese girl wearing a kimono. Despite her beauty, her katana has claimed many heads.

Name: Wodan the Resident of the Forest
Description: A small, pink-faced creature that is enmeshed in thorns. It can power itself up by drawing on all plants on the own field.

Name: Guardian of the Labyrinth
Description: A daunting warrior that guards the gates of the Labyrinth. It cuts down mercilessly anyone without the authority to pass.

Name: Haniwa
Description: An animated earthenware figurine from an ancient time. It guards treasures in a tomb of a king from long ago.

Name: Yashinoki
Description: An animated palm tree that developed its own sense of being. It attacks by dropping coconuts that contain tasty juice.

Name: Vishwar Randi
Description: A female warrior who pledged her allegiance to darkness. She lives to slaughter all those opposed to her ideals.

Name: The Drdek
Description: A boggling monster of an eyeball from which grows a foot. To attack, it leaps high and strikes with its sharp talons.

Name: Dark Assailant
Description: A terrifying assassin that reigns over the world of darkness. It is armed with a blade named Psycho Sword.

Name: Candle of Fate
Description: A sinister candle in the form of a hand that decides destiny. It decides its foe's fate when the flame goes out.

Name: Water Element
Description: A delicate and feminine elemental that makes its home in water. She obscures visibility by enveloping her surroundings with a fog.

Name: Dissolverock
Description: A bloblike monster that emerged into life from magma. It is so intensely hot, it melts anything coming too close.

Name: Meda Bat
Description: A fiendish flying eye created by an evil-hearted soul. It attacks by raining Dark Bombs on its foes.

Name: One Who Hunts Souls
Description: A headless, centaurlike creature armed with a wicked sword. The sword steals souls from those it cuts.

Name: Root Water
Description: An amphibian creature that avoids notice by lurking in the waves. It creates massive, dark tidal waves to attack.

Name: Master & Expert
Description: A pair of an expert beast tamer and the totally loyal beast. The combination they form is perfect.

Name: Water Omotics
Description: A maiden who controls water flowing endlessly from her vase. She changes the water into a dragon to attack.

Name: Hyo
Description: A fearsome warrior whose body is made entirely of ice. It freezes everything that it comes into contact with.

Name: Enchanting Mermaid
Description: A mermaid that is very beautiful, but also terribly cruel. She enchants seafarers and draws them to watery graves.

Name: Nekogal #1
Description: A classy and beautiful spirit of a cat with a long tail. Despite her appearance, she is vicious and claws foes in a blur.

Name: Fairywitch
Description: A disgraced being that had refuted her duty to become an angel. Instead, she followed her heart and became a witch.

Name: Embryonic Beast
Description: A pitifully ugly fiend that failed to become fully mature. It inhales all things with the hole on its belly.

Name: Prevent Rat
Description: A beast with a tough, blue shell made of hair bunched together. The shell gives it a high degree of protection.

Name: Dimensional Warrior
Description: A young warrior who can slice open a seam in the dimensions. He then traps the foe in the opened dimensional rift.

Name: Stone Armadiller
Description: A monster covered all over by hair of rocklike hardness. It is well protected from injury.

Name: Beastking of the Swamps
Description: A terribly slimy being that makes its lair in boggy swamps. It can pull all monsters on the field and drown them in a swamp.

Name: Ancient Sorcerer
Description: A masked sorcerer from long ago that bears numerous rods. He wields the various rods to affect many kinds of attacks.

Name: Lunar Queen Elzaim
Description: A lovely winged goddess who stands guard over the moon. She blocks attacks with a curtain of moonlight.

Name: Wicked Mirror
Description: A fiendish mirror that hypnotizes all that peer into its depths. By putting its foes to sleep, it can avoid having to fight.

Name: The Little Swordsman of Aile
Description: A minute but loyal warrior who serves the famed traveler Aile. He rides his lizard steed into battle.

Name: Rock Ogre Grotto #2
Description: A golem that emerged when boulders and rocks gathered together. In battle, it petrifies, then destroys the foe.

Name: Wing Egg Elf
Description: A tiny elf with wings that keeps out of sight in an egg shell. It uses its relatively big wings to parry attacks.

Name: The Furious Sea King
Description: A magnificent ruler of the seas and master of waves. It creates endless tidal waves that swallow all before it.

Name: Princess of Tsurugi
Description: A princess who is skilled at the use and handling of many swords. Indeed, her sword-fighting ability is considerable.

Name: Unknown Warrior of Fiend
Description: A nameless warrior whose arm is in the form of a sword. It creates a vacuum at high speed to tear at the foe.

Name: Sectarian of Secrets
Description: A hooded sorcerer who pledged loyal allegiance to darkness. It summons a fiend's hand that drags its victims into darkness.

Name: Versago the Destroyer
Description: A dark god of destruction that was born in the realm of darkness. It attacks by summoning a destructive storm.

Name: Wetha
Description: A diminutive elemental that has the power to manipulate rain. It summons wild typhoons that blow most things away.

Name: Megirus Light
Description: A creepy fiend with blue eyes that shine with an ill light. The evil light of its eyes inflicts damage.

Name: Mavelus
Description: A type of a fiery bird that makes its home in high mountains. It sprays fire from its mouth to burn everything around it.

Name: Ancient Tree of Enlightenment
Description: An ancient tree that grew enlightened over many long years. It uses its vast knowledge to avoid many kinds of attack.

Name: Green Phantom King
Description: A young king who rules over lush, green, and thriving forests. It makes its home among verdant trees.

Name: Ground Attacker Bugroth
Description: A military robot made for undertaking combat on the ground. It appears to have been usable in the sea, but no longer.

Name: Ray & Temperature
Description: A friendly and supportive twosome of the north wind and the sun. They attack with cutting winds and a harsh thermal ray.

Name: Gorgon Egg
Description: An egg laid by a Gorgon with a single eye at its center. Whatever the eye reflects is what will hatch from the egg.

Name: Petit Moth
Description: A minute insect larva with numerous eyelike markings. It is impossible to tell what it would look like when it is grown.

Name: King Fog
Description: A fiend that expertly hides itself among obscuring smoke. It enshrouds itself with smoke, making it impossible to see.

Name: Protector of the Throne
Description: A princess who guards the king's throne from foes in his absence. She is very well protected against harm.

Name: Mystic Clown
Description: A bizarre creature with many eyes that attacks as if demented. It cannot be stopped in its crazed rampage by anyone.

Name: Mystical Sheep #2
Description: A sheep with a long tail from which dangles a pendulum. It swings the pendulum to hypnotize its foes into sleeping.

Name: Holograh
Description: A floating robot with a projection system on its bottom. It confuses foes with many illusions and strikes with no warning.

Name: Tao the Chanter
Description: A devious spell caster that merges yin and yang together. It does so to create a distorted force.

Name: Serpent Marauder
Description: An enormous snake that has a single eye and massive fangs. It exhales a frigid breath that encases foes in ice.

Name: Gatekeeper
Description: A vigilant and combative machine made to guard a portal. Its durable construction makes it tough to destroy.

Name: Ogre of the Black Shadow
Description: A foul ogre that has been possessed by a malevolent shadow. It charges foes at an astounding speed.

Name: Dark Artist
Description: A malignant being that practices the dark art of evil. It crushes foes under a succession of artistic objects.

Name: Change Slime
Description: A gelatinous slime that has an eye that protrudes from its body. It freely alters its body to assume a variety of guises.

Name: Moon Envoy
Description: A striking warrior who serves the goddess of the moon. He uses a pole arm with a quartermoon blade.

Name: Fireyarou
Description: An imposing genie that sits serenely while engulfed in flames. It attacks by freely controlling the surrounding flames.

Name: Psychic Kappa
Description: A traditional Japanese monster with amphibian qualities. It avoids taking damage through the use of psychic powers.

Name: Masaki the Legendary Swordsman
Description: A legendary swordsman who wears a huge and thick suit of armor. He is said to have killed a hundred men like him.

Name: Dragoness the Wicked Knight
Description: A winged knight that gained power through dragon equipment. It hacks at foes from the sky, diving repeatedly.

Name: Bio Plant
Description: A hideous monstrosity of a plant with many eyes and legs. It was made as a result of an experiment gone horribly wrong.

Name: One-Eyed Shield Dragon
Description: A birdlike dragon with one eye and a shield on its belly. The shield is used for both defense and attack.

Name: Cyber Soldier of Darkworld
Description: A mechanical warrior that was built with the powers of darkness. It destroys its foes with demented determination.

Name: Wicked Dragon with the Ersatz Head
Description: A massive winged dragon with a face growing on its stomach. It chews up foes using both of its mouths.

Name: Sonic Maid
Description: A beautiful maiden who is adept at the manipulation of sounds. She attacks with a scythe in the form of a musical note.

Name: Kurama
Description: A strange bird creature with wings, a long tail and arms. It attacks foes from the sky using the tail.

Name: Yaranzo
Description: A wickedly devious being that guards a treasure chest from within. It leaps out and attacks anyone trying to open the chest.

Name: Kanan the Swordmistress
Description: A female swordsman in armor wielding a sword and shield. She floats like a butterfly and stings like a bee.

Name: Takriminos
Description: A relative of sea serpents that has fins on its body. It can move about freely in water.

Name: Stuffed Animal
Description: A deceptive monster that is disguised as an adorable teddy bear. It bites the unwary with its zippered mouth.

Name: Megasonic Eye
Description: A killing machine that came from the far reaches of space. It is made of a mysterious metal.

Name: Super War-Lion
Description: An extremely vicious lion beast with sharp, hooked claws. It cruelly tears apart foes with its wicked claws.

Name: Yamadron
Description: A spiked dragon with three heads that breathe fire. It sets its surroundings ablaze in a sea of flames.

Name: Seiyaryu
Description: A sacred, small-winged dragon endowed with divine power. Breathing a sacred fire, it incinerates minions of evil.

Name: Three-Legged Zombies
Description: A skeletal pair of comrades, one thin and one fat. They appear to have some trouble walking in unison.

Name: Zera The Mant
Description: An extremely strong and evil monster of imposing size. It attacks with its bulk and horribly hooked claws.

Name: Flying Penguin
Description: A rare kind of penguin that has the ability to fly. For flight, it uses a pair of wings that look like ears.

Name: Millennium Shield
Description: One of the infamous and eagerly sought Millennium items. It is said to withstand any attack, however hard.

Name: Fairy's Gift
Description: A diminutive green fairy that flies on the wings of a butterfly. It can cast a spell to restore LP by 1,000.

Name: Black Luster Soldier
Description: The strongest of all warriors, it suitably wears black. It equals the Blue-Eyes White Dragon in ability.

Name: Fiend's Mirror
Description: A diabolical mirror that harbors dark and terrible secrets. It draws in and entraps all that it reflects on its surface.

Name: Labyrinth Wall
Description: A strictly defensive card that depicts a labyrinth made of stone. It creates walls on the field, forming a maze without an exit.

Name: Jirai Gumo
Description: A stealthy spider that lurks out of sight under the ground. It makes prey out of anything that passes over its lair.

Name: Shadow Ghoul
Description: A creepy zombie that drags itself around in darkness. It becomes a dangerous adversary in the dark.

Name: Wall Shadow
Description: A green-skinned zombie that scuttles quickly along walls. It attacks at incredible speeds.

Name: Labyrinth Tank
Description: A powerhouse machine found in labyrinths. It can be powered up based on the number of Labyrinth Walls on the own field.

Name: Sanga of the Thunder
Description: A powerful deity that represents the element of thunder. It can join Kazejin and Suijin to become a Gate Guardian.

Name: Kazejin
Description: A powerful deity that represents the element of wind. It can join Sanga and Suijin to become a Gate Guardian.

Name: Suijin
Description: A powerful deity that represents the element of water. It can join Sanga and Kazejin to become a Gate Guardian.

Name: Gate Guardian
Description: A combined being that consists of Sanga, Kazejin and Suijin. Its powers place it among the strongest of all beings.

Name: Dungeon Worm
Description: A gargantuan worm that lurks underground in labyrinths. It swallows anyone walking above it whole with its huge mouth.

Name: Monster Tamer
Description: A warrior who is skilled at handling Dungeon Worms in duels. He can power up all Dungeon Worms on the player's field.

Name: Ryu-Kishin Powered
Description: A Ryu-Kishin that has been grown stronger by the power of darkness. Beware of its cruelly hooked talons.

Name: Swordstalker
Description: A malevolent warrior that embodies the fury of fallen comrades. Its heart blazes with vengeance.

Name: La Jinn the Mystical Genie of the Lamp
Description: An obeisant genie that keeps hidden in a magical lamp. It grants any wish of the master who has summoned it.

Name: Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon
Description: The ultimate of all dragons that has three awe-inspiring heads. It is formed by three Blue-Eyes White Dragons.

Name: Toon Alligator
Description: A cartoony alligator that has big eyes, large teeth, and an axe. It emerged from the world of American comic books.

Name: Rude Kaiser
Description: A savage beast warrior that bears a pair of prized axes. Blows from the two axes are quite powerful.

Name: Parrot Dragon
Description: A sharp - beaked dragon from the world of American comics. Don't be taken in by its adorable appearance.

Name: Dark Rabbit
Description: A comedic rabbit from the world of American comics. It darts and dashes about very quickly.

Name: Bickuribox
Description: A birdlike fiend that hides inside a Jack-in-the-box case. It springs out without warning to strike.

Name: Harpie's Pet Dragon
Description: A ferocious dragon that is said to only obey the will of Harpies. For anyone else, it is too dangerous to treat as a pet.

Name: Mystic Lamp
Description: An enchanted lamp that has a special power despite its stats. Its attack power can be used to damage the opponent directly.

Name: Pendulum Machine
Description: A horrifying machine made for torture with a huge blade. It swings the blade like a pendulum to slice victims in half.

Name: Giltia the D. Knight
Description: A sorcererlike knight who uses magic to attack his foes. He bears a spear that is said to steal the souls of victims.

Name: Launcher Spider
Description: A mechanical spider that is fitted with a pair of rocket launchers. It fires its rockets in barrages that obliterate the targets.

Name: Zoa
Description: A fiendish monster that can be made even more powerful. It reaches full potential by becoming metalized as a machine.

Name: Metalzoa
Description: A Zoa that has undergone metalization into a deadly machine. Its attack power is extremely high.

Name: Zone Eater
Description: A buoyant sea cucumber that drifts aimlessly in water. It sucks in enemies and slowly digests them.

Name: Steel Scorpion
Description: A mechanical scorpion that hacks away with razorlike pincers. Beware of the damage its steel axes can inflict.

Name: Dancing Elf
Description: An angelic elf that reels and dances in the sky to music. The wings also serve as sharp blades.

Name: Ocubeam
Description: A fearsome being that keeps watch with big ears and eye. Despite its terrifying appearance, it is a fairy.

Name: Leghul
Description: A monstrous worm that has a special power despite its stats. Its attack power can be used to damage the opponent directly.

Name: Ooguchi
Description: A monster bullfrog with a grotesquely stretched mouth. Touching the spikes on its back causes numbness.

Name: Swordsman from a Foreign Land
Description: A swordsman who has come from a land far off in the Orient. He bears a sinister sword that is said to tear apart darkness.

Name: Emperor of the Land and Sea
Description: A monstrous reptile whose enormous mouth brims with sharp teeth. It blasts fire in all directions from its mouth.

Name: Ushi Oni
Description: A brutal ox fiend that was resurrected using dark sorcery. It emerges from a vase when it is summoned.

Name: Monster Eye
Description: A sneaky familiar that spies on foes from a variety of places. It has the ability to reveal the cards in the foe's hand.

Name: Leogun
Description: A lion with a magnificent mane suitable for the king of beasts. Its body is similarly formidable.

Name: Tatsunootoshigo
Description: A bizarre monster with the torso of a horse and a fish's tail. It gallops through the sea as if it were the wind.

Name: Saber Slasher
Description: A murderous machine that wields a pair of curved swords. It rampages uncontrollably while holding the swords high.

Name: Yaiba Robo
Description: A thresherlike machine that conceals blades in its cube body. In battle, it extends the blades to chop everything to bits.

Name: Machine King
Description: A gigantic combat robot constructed of a super-metal alloy. It looses Fire Blasts from its arms.

Name: Giant Mech-Soldier
Description: A towering mechanical soldier armed with a massive axe. It is so powerful, one blow of its axe can split the ground.

Name: Metal Dragon
Description: A mechanized dragon whose body gleams in a glittering silver. Be prepared against its fiery breath.

Name: Mechanical Spider
Description: A spiderlike monster that operates on a system like clockwork. It attacks using sickles at the tips of its feet.

Name: Bat
Description: A mechanical bat that is used to undertake bombing missions. It carries bombs under its wings.

Name: Giga-Tech Wolf
Description: A barbarous wolf whose entire body is constructed of steel. It bites and tears at foes with sharply pointed fangs.

Name: Cyber Soldier
Description: A mechanical soldier that serves the Machine King as a guard. It rolls its round body to quickly reach enemies.

Name: Shovel Crusher
Description: A lionlike machine with both hands ending in wide shovels. Beware of the shovels as they can crush anything.

Name: Mechanicalchaser
Description: A robotic hunter that capably serves the Machine King. It pursues its targets relentlessly until they are caught.

Name: Blocker
Description: A peculiar machine made up of a jumble of parts that are weapons. The parts separate and attack in a swarm.

Name: Blast Juggler
Description: A mechanical monster that has the body of a time bomb. Above all else it loves to explode.

Name: Golgoil
Description: A massively armored robot constructed of tempered steel. It emerges from a hole that leads to another dimension.

Name: Giganto
Description: A daunting machine that is equipped with a spiked iron ball. It charges at foes while swinging the ball wildly.

Name: Cyber-Stein
Description: An entirely evil machine created in an underground laboratory. It launches missiles from its mouth.

Name: Cyber Commander
Description: A combat-ready fighting machine with a large arsenal of weapons. Included in the arsenal are a rocket launcher and a bazooka.

Name: Jinzo #7
Description: A manmade human that is under development in a secret lab. On occasion, it goes out of control.

Name: Dice Armadillo
Description: A mechanized armadillo that can roll itself up for protection. Rolled up, it takes on the shape of a die.

Name: Sky Dragon
Description: A birdlike dragon that keeps itself airborne on four wings. It uses the blade-edged wings to attack.

Name: Thunder Dragon
Description: An airborne dragon that can summon angry thunder clouds. It strikes foes with huge bolts of lightning.

Name: Stone D.
Description: A rugged dragon whose entire body is composed of boulders. Because of its rocky build, its blows are heavy.

Name: Kaiser Dragon
Description: The emperor of all dragons has batlike wings and huge pride. Befitting its status, its attacks are powerful.

Name: Magician of Faith
Description: A female magician whose immaturity makes her weak. She banishes darkness with sacred spells.

Name: Goddess of Whim
Description: A female deity who is known for her unpredictably fickle ways. She can sacrifice herself in exchange for drawing a new card.

Name: Water Magician
Description: A young magician who can make water behave as he desires. He surrounds foes with a wall of water and engulfs them.

Name: Ice Water
Description: A blazingly red-haired mermaid with an aggressive nature. It attacks using the spikes that grow from its body.

Name: Waterdragon Fairy
Description: An aqueous fairy that aimlessly wanders about in water. It appears to be capable of summoning a sea dragon.

Name: Ancient Elf
Description: An elf that has lived for thousands upon thousands of years. It controls elementals to attack foes.

Name: Beautiful Beast Trainer
Description: A ravishing female beast trainer whose gender makes her rare. When she has her whip in hand, her very personality changes.

Name: Water Girl
Description: A beautiful girl with fins on her arms in a revealing outfit. She attacks by hurling ice as if they were spears.

Name: White Dolphin
Description: A pure-white dolphin that has a single horn on its head. It attacks by generating huge waves.

Name: Deepsea Shark
Description: A horribly vicious shark that savagely attacks any opponent. Anything in the water is fair game for an unprovoked attack.

Name: Metal Fish
Description: A fish that is constructed of metal with a sharp cutter as its tail. It chops up opponents with its tail fin.

Name: Bottom Dweller
Description: A fish deity that swims with a regal sense of elegance. Angering it is dangerously foolish.

Name: 7 Colored Fish
Description: An extremely rare fish in the seven colors of a rainbow. Capturing it is not a feat to be taken lightly.

Name: Mech Bass
Description: A mechanized bass with a large mouth and a cannon on its back. The cannon fires blinding plasma rays.

Name: Aqua Dragon
Description: A furtive dragon that lurks quietly out of sight underwater. It attacks by shooting blocks of water from its mouth.

Name: Sea King Dragon
Description: The king of the sea, this dragon has a tortoiselike shell. It sprays foam from its mouth to attack.

Name: Turu-Purun
Description: A peculiar, one-eyed creature with a gelatinous build. It skewers foes with a single jab of its harpoon.

Name: Guardian of the Sea
Description: A single-eyed merman that serves as the protector of the seas. It punishes anyone that pollutes the sea without mercy.

Name: Aqua Snake
Description: An aqueous snake with the eyes of a bug and an orb on its tail. The orb is used to hypnotize foes so that they drown.

Name: Giant Red Seasnake
Description: A snakelike monster with a striped body that lives in water. It will try to bite anyone that ventures too close.

Name: Spike Seadra
Description: A maned sea dragon that has spikes on its body for skewering. Once they are embedded in the foe, it discharges electricity.

Name: 30,000-Year White Turtle
Description: A gigantic white turtle that has lived for 30,000 years. It is highly protected from damage.

Name: Kappa Avenger
Description: A traditional Japanese monster that lives only for revenge. It sold its soul to evil for avenging the deaths of friends.

Name: Kanikabuto
Description: A strange crab creature that has a pair of huge pincers. It chops up its foes using the pincers.

Name: Zarigun
Description: A hulking monster with pincers that evolved from a crayfish. It aims for its opponent's neck with its large pincers.

Name: Millennium Golem
Description: A craggy Golem that had been made the guardian of treasures. For over a thousand years, it fulfilled its duty.

Name: Destroyer Golem
Description: A massively muscled Golem recognized by an overgrown right arm. It mashes down its foes with the big hand to cause damage.

Name: Barrel Rock
Description: A rock-hard monster with machine guns mounted on its shoulders. It rams foes while shooting the machine guns steadily.

Name: Minomushi Warrior
Description: A hardy warrior that is completely encased in a rock armor. It swings around a heavy sword hewn out of stone.

Name: Stone Ghost
Description: A rock-bound monster whose head erupts if it becomes enraged. On eruption, it sends down a shower of boulders and rocks.

Name: Kaminari Attack
Description: An electric deity that looks down on earth from the heavens. It smites evil-doers with bolts of lightning.

Name: Tripwire Beast
Description: A peculiar four-legged creature with its head on the ground. It generates powerful waves of electromagnetism to attack.

Name: Bolt Escargot
Description: An enormous snail that spits a gooey, immobilizing fluid. After making the foe unable to move, it attacks with electricity.

Name: Bolt Penguin
Description: A penguin with electric whips in the place of its wings. It stuns its foe with electricity, then garrotes them.

Name: The Immortal of Thunder
Description: A kindly-looking being that actually is very quick to anger. It has no qualms about hitting anyone with a bolt of lightning.

Name: Electric Snake
Description: A cobra that generates electricity from all over its body. It stores power inside an orb at the end of its tail.

Name: Wing Eagle
Description: A predatory bird that searches for prey from high altitudes. It never fails to catch prey that it has targeted.

Name: Punished Eagle
Description: An eagle that renders judgments from a lofty position. It punishes those it finds guilty with silver talons.

Name: Skull Red Bird
Description: A deceptive bird that conceals knives among its feathers. It drops the knives on foes to attack.

Name: Crimson Sunbird
Description: An inferno of a bird that blazes wildly in crimson all over. It looses a shower of embers with every flap of its wings.

Name: Queen Bird
Description: An imposing bird with a cranelike neck supporting its large head. The highly protected bird pecks with its large beak to attack.

Name: Armed Ninja
Description: A stealthy ninja who is colored blue entirely from head to toe. He attacks with a large sickle and his spiked feet.

Name: Magical Ghost
Description: A female ghost that casts spells on foes during battle. Her spells sow terror and confusion among foes.

Name: Soul Hunter
Description: A fiendish clown that rides upon a monstrous lizard. The lizard eats the souls of all enemies felled by the clown.

Name: Air Eater
Description: A many-armed fiend that can inhale air to create an airless state. By doing so, it suffocates its foes.

Name: Vermillion Sparrow
Description: A fearsome warrior who is engulfed in roaring flames. The flames give off intense heat.

Name: Sea Kamen
Description: A cold and cruel monster that battles with immense claws. It savagely tears apart foes without hesitation.

Name: Sinister Serpent
Description: A venomous serpent that takes to the skies on its wings. It is inept at slithering on the ground, however.

Name: Ganigumo
Description: A spider that has a wicked pair of hard, crablike pincers. It ensnares its foes with its silk, then attacks with its pincers.

Name: Alinsection
Description: A large stag beetle whose large pincer is edged with saw blades. Its forelegs also serve as rasping saws.

Name: Insect Soldiers of the Sky
Description: A soldier among insects that possess the ability to fly. It gathers in an angry swarm with others to raid enemies.

Name: Cockroach Knight
Description: A gigantic cockroach that is equipped with a sword and armor. It can show up anywhere from shadows and confined spaces.

Name: Kuwagata A
Description: A ferocious stag beetle encased within a craggy hard shell. Beware of its guillotine cutter attack that aims for the neck.

Name: Burglar
Description: A cunning, treacherous mouse with an outsized left claw arm. It uses the large claw to attack.

Name: Pragtical
Description: A dinosaur with spikes on its long tail and atop its head. The attacks it throws with the spikes are very strong. Beware.

Name: Garvas
Description: A ferocious lion beast that has a powerful set of wings. It is the embodiment of evil.

Name: Ameba
Description: A gelatinous monster that engulfs prey completely from above. It digests the trapped prey slowly to cause damage.

Name: Korogashi
Description: A high-power dung beetle that can roll dung larger than itself. It crushes its foes with its massive ball of dung.

Name: Boo Koo
Description: A strange magician that has taken the form of a book. Printed in its pages are spells of all kinds.

Name: Flower Wolf
Description: A wolflike beast that is covered all over with flowers. The flowers spin around while it is attacking.

Name: Rainbow Flower
Description: A one-eyed flower monster whose petals are in rainbow colors. It lunges and bites at anyone getting too close.

Name: Barrel Lily
Description: "A dangerous lily that acts very much like a nature-made pistol. It attacks by shooting ""bullets"" of pollen."

Name: Needle Ball
Description: A ball-like fiend that is fully studded with sharp needles. It falls out of the sky in a cluster with many others.

Name: Peacock
Description: An oversized peacock with a breathtaking profusion of feathers. It shoots its beautiful feathers to attack.

Name: Hoshiningen
Description: A peculiar being with the ability to power up light element monsters and power down shadow types on the own field.

Name: Maha Vailo
Description: A magician who is always dressed in an outfit of navy blue. He always sits cross-legged and meditates.

Name: Rainbow Marine Mermaid
Description: A reticent mermaid who appears only on very rare occasions. She emerges only when a large rainbow arches across the sky.

Name: Musician King
Description: A musical master whose guitar playing is unmatched by others. He attacks by generating ultrasonic waves.

Name: Wilmee
Description: A seemingly adorable bunny known for its cruel, vicious nature. It tears its foes apart with its sharp and hooked claws.

Name: Yado Karu
Description: A hermit crab monster that has the head of a dragon. It withdraws itself into the shell to take refuge.

Name: Morinphen
Description: A freakish winged fiend with a pointed head like that of a fish. Its long arms end in hooked talons.

Name: Kattapillar
Description: An insect larva that spits strands of silk to attack. It is not known what kind of insect it will grow into.

Name: Dragon Seeker
Description: An enormous fiend that is a scourge to dragons of all kinds. It can destroy every dragon on the opponent's field.

Name: Man-Eater Bug
Description: A hulking insect whose forelegs end in awesome pincers. It chops up foes with its pincers and eats voraciously.

Name: D. Human
Description: A mortal warrior who has the power of dragons in him. He wields a sword crafted from the fang of a dragon.

Name: Turtle Raccoon
Description: A rotund little raccoon that shoulders a large turtle shell. It tricks foes using transformation and illusion techniques.

Name: Fungi of the Musk
Description: A plant that secretes a highly potent acid onto its surface. The powerful acid dissolves anyone that gets too near.

Name: Prisman
Description: A statuesque being that is composed of high-clarity crystals. It collects and concentrates light to fire laser beams.

Name: Gale Dogra
Description: A stinger-equipped moth that has toxic dust coating its wings. It whips up tornadoes of toxic dust by flying around.

Name: Crazy Fish
Description: A maniacal flying fish whose head comes to a sharp point. It leaps at foes with its head thrust forward.

Name: Cyber Saurus
Description: A machine in the form of a dinosaur with mismatched arms. One arm is fitted with a beam weapon.

Name: Bracchio-raidus
Description: A gargantuan dinosaur that has a thick and elongated neck. It stomps on anything that it discovers moving near its feet.

Name: Laughing Flower
Description: A bizarre flowering plant that laughs without stop. Hearing its laughter for too long leads to confusion.

Name: Bean Soldier
Description: A courageous plant warrior that attacks with a knife and beans. Be careful - it is stronger than it looks.

Name: Cannon Soldier
Description: A fiendish machine that is equipped with a topside cannon. Its attack power is on the high side.

Name: Guardian of the Throne Room
Description: A robot that fulfills its guardian role with missile launchers. Its homing missiles track targets until they strike.

Name: Brave Scizzar
Description: A fiendish robot that brandishes two sets of cutter systems. The numerous cutters are manipulated dextrously to chop foes.

Name: The Statue of Easter Island
Description: An ancient Moai statue similar to the ones on Easter Island. It looses rings of slow-moving laser energy from its mouth.

Name: Muka Muka
Description: An extremely irritating bug that annoys foes into huge rages. It is adept at goading the furious foes into going out of control.

Name: Sand Stone
Description: A subterranean monster that ambushes unsuspecting foes. It attacks the startled enemies with its tentacles.

Name: Boulder Tortoise
Description: A ponderous tortoise whose entire body is composed of boulders. Its defense rating is outstanding.

Name: Fire Kraken
Description: A huge squid engulfed in a spectacularly blazing wall of fire. The flames writhe out of control even underwater.

Name: Turtle Bird
Description: A precious turtle whose wings enable it to take flight. It lives in water for the most part, however.

Name: Skullbird
Description: A malevolent bird that exhales a foul and corrupted breath. Inhaling its breath is said to cost the victim his soul.

Name: Monstrous Bird
Description: A somewhat rarely seen bird of the most amazing size. It dives on foes at sharp angles to strike.

Name: The Bistro Butcher
Description: A fiendish gourmet chef that has a hook on one arm. It cooks and savors every foe it fells, no matter what.

Name: Star Boy
Description: An extraterrestrial life form from the far reaches of space. It appears to enjoy life in water.

Name: Spirit of the Mountain
Description: An elderly magician that raises mountains with his flute. He has the power to turn the field into a mountain.

Name: Neck Hunter
Description: A cyclopean fiend that decapitates foes with its scythe. It can also shoot a beam of energy from its eye.

Name: Milus Radiant
Description: A deceptive beast that appears to be the picture of cuteness. However, it is cruel and vicious in reality.

Name: Togex
Description: A spike-equipped beast that is surprisingly fast and agile. It rolls up into a ball and rams its enemies.

Name: Flame Cerebrus
Description: A triple-headed dog that is ablaze all over its body. It executes foes with the fires of the underworld.

Name: Eldeen
Description: A young, magician who wields a staff bearing a blue gemstone. She attacks with a variety of spells with her staff.

Name: Mystical Sand
Description: A horrifying witch that can turn anything she desires into stone. The victims crumble away i nto sand.

Name: Gemini Elf
Description: Twin elven sisters who practice in the ways of magic. They take turns while they attack.

Name: Kwagar Hercules
Description: A hybrid insect of a stag beetle and a horned beetle. It has the former's mandibles and the latter's huge horn.

Name: Minar
Description: A two-horned insect monster that has two pairs of forelegs. Each of the arms moves independently for attacking.

Name: Kamakiriman
Description: A praying mantis monster that stands erect like a human. It attacks using the two scythelike forelegs.

Name: Mechaleon
Description: A large chameleon with the ability to alter its body coloring. Using this ability, it can conceal itself in any location.

Name: Mega Thunderball
Description: A tricolored ball of many spikes that rolls around on its own. While it is rolling, it releases jolts of electrical charges.

Name: Niwatori
Description: A gargantuan bird that can swallow its enemies whole and alive. It absorbs what it eats as its energy.

Name: Corroding Shark
Description: A putrefying zombie shark that wanders aimlessly on the seas. It casts a death curse on those it encounters.

Name: Skelengel
Description: An invisible fairy on which only the halo and wings can be seen. It has the ability to draw a card from the deck.

Name: Hane-Hane
Description: A beast with a prominent nose and an axe of huge dimensions. It whips up gusts to stop its foes, then attacks with the axe.

Name: Misairuzame
Description: A spiny fish that has sharp spikes growing all over its body. It launches missiles from its belly.

Name: Tongyo
Description: A vampiric fish that uses its tongue to capture other fish. It then uses the elongated tongue to drain the prey of energy.

Name: Dharma Cannon
Description: A mechanical dharma that is jam-packed with an array of cannons. Once it sets its sights on a target, it never misses.

Name: Skelgon
Description: A zombie dragon of which little remains but its bones. Despite its skeletal state, it can fly.

Name: Wow Warrior
Description: A beastly fish that has grown arms and legs like a reptile. It bites at foes with its sharp fangs.

Name: Griggle
Description: A small, odd plant creature with an unruly mass of leaves on its head. It twirls around to attack with the leaves and flick seeds.

Name: Bone Mouse
Description: A vengeful mouse that came back from the dead as a zombie. Its purpose is to exact revenge on the cat that killed it.

Name: Frog the Jam
Description: A furtive slime that is in the shape of a frog's head. It attacks by singing loudly in an awful croak.

Name: Behegon
Description: A sea serpent known for its peculiar behavior and appearance. It is noted for its large mouth and tusks.

Name: Dark Elf
Description: A black-hearted elf that loves to fight above all else. It can be a troublesome enemy if it gets to strike first.

Name: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #2
Description: A dragonlike bird that uses its wings for attacking foes. By flapping its wings, it generates wild tornadoes.

Name: Mushroom Man #2
Description: The grown form of Mushroom Man is a mix of a tree and fungus. Its attack power is much higher than the original guise.

Name: Lava Battleguard
Description: A brutal warrior with two horns and a wild mass of hair. It powers up Swamp Battleguards on the player's field.

Name: Tyhone #2
Description: A fiery red dragon that looses fireballs from its mouth. It turns its surroundings into a blazing sea of flames.

Name: The Wandering Doomed
Description: A staggering skeleton that failed to pass on to the hereafter. It wanders without aim or purpose.

Name: Steel Ogre Grotto #1
Description: A gargantuan steel statue of a deity revered among machines. The statue is said to be worshipped in the kingdom of machines.

Name: Pot the Trick
Description: A familiar that loyally obeys every command of a magician. It is not particularly strong in any way.

Name: Oscillo Hero
Description: A baffling sort of a warrior with a single eye and antennas. It arrived from another dimension.

Name: Invader from Another Dimension
Description: An insectlike fiend that has claw arms and large eyes. It came to earth from beyond the Milky Way.

Name: Lesser Dragon
Description: A low-class dragon that is simply not particularly strong. It does not even have a breath attack.

Name: Needle Worm
Description: An insect larva that has three sharp steel spikes on its head. Don't underestimate what this monster could do.

Name: Wretched Ghost of the Attic
Description: A diminutive fiend that hides in the attic of any house. It does not cause too much mischief.

Name: Great Mammoth of Goldfine
Description: A zombie mammoth whose bones gleam in a dazzling gold. It is very rare sight to behold.

Name: Man-eating Black Shark
Description: A voracious shark colored black that has a pair of arms. It senses the scent of humans in the sea and races to attack.

Name: Yormungarde
Description: A dragonlike serpent that appears in the world of myths. It is known for its extreme length.

Name: Darkworld Thorns
Description: A fiendish plant with vines that exists in the darkworld. It ensnares anyone that tries to force their way through.

Name: Anthrosaurus
Description: A standing dinosaur that has the build like that of humans. While it is highly intelligent, it is not very strong.

Name: Drooling Lizard
Description: A snake that has assumed a humanoid guise and a thirst for blood. It attacks people in the open, under the cover of darkness.

Name: Trakadon
Description: A ferocious dinosaur that wears stripes like those of a tiger. It sprints through wastelands at an impressive pace.

Name: B. Dragon Jungle King
Description: A jet-black dragon that makes its home in dense jungles. Its huge teeth enable it to crunch and devour trees.

Name: Empress Judge
Description: The majestic empress of a land of gold, and also a stern judge. No one can defy whatever judgment she renders.

Name: Little D
Description: An infant tyrannosaur that is tough in its own regard. Its nature is vicious in the extreme.

Name: Witch of the Black Forest
Description: A seemingly young witch who lives deep in a dense forest. With the eye in the forehead, she sees the truth.

Name: Ancient One of the Deep Forest
Description: A white goat that has lived in a forest for many, many years. It is also known as the ancient sage of the forest.

Name: Giant Scorpion of the Tundra
Description: A rarely seen scorpion that lives in tundras, not deserts. Perhaps befitting its cold habitat, its shell is a bright blue.

Name: Crow Goblin
Description: A winged goblin that is knowledgeable on numerous subjects. It is said to possess telekinetic powers.

Name: Leo Wizard
Description: A mysterious magician that cloaks itself with a black cape. Its identity is a talking lion beast.

Name: Abyss Flower
Description: A rarely seen flower of symmetry with a thorny stem. It grows silently in deep darkness out of light's reach.

Name: Patrol Robo
Description: A state-of-the-art robot that was made for security purposes. It destroys intruders the instant it locates them.

Name: Takuhee
Description: A glittering gold bird that is considered to be a bad omen. Its appearance always presages a tragedy.

Name: Dark Witch
Description: A warlike fairy who appears in myths from ancient times. Her spear brings divine retribution to the unjust.

Name: Living Vase
Description: An animated floral vase that scatters pollen from its flowers. While it is scattering pollen, it lunges and bites.

Name: Tentacle Plant
Description: A carnivorous plant that has an outgrowth of tentacles. It attacks anyone nearby by extending its tentacles.

Name: Beaked Snake
Description: A massive constrictor snake with an impressive beak. It binds its foe with its long body and pecks away unopposed.

Name: Morphing Jar
Description: A curious jar in which hides a being with a single eye. The being leaps out to attack the unwary who get too close.

Name: Muse-A
Description: An ethereal and artistic fairy known for her harp playing. When it comes to the harp, she is far beyond compare.

Name: Giant Turtle Who Feeds on Flames
Description: An enormous turtle whose bright red shell bristles with spikes. It is said to feed on fire.

Name: Rose Spectre of Dunn
Description: A dark being that makes its home among beautiful rose flowers. It drains the souls of its victims to feed the plant.

Name: Fiend Reflection #1
Description: A dragon-winged beast that carries a mysterious mirror. It can draw its foes into the mirror's world.

Name: Ghoul with an Appetite
Description: A pointy-eared zombie that has an appetite without limit. It never becomes full, regardless of how much it eats.

Name: Pale Beast
Description: A creepy, blue-skinned beast with a pair of horns on its head. The identity of this beast is completely unknown.

Name: Little Chimera
Description: A monster that came from an experiment to grow wings on a beast. Despite its appearance, it is not very strong.

Name: Violent Rain
Description: An aqueous monster that takes the form of a thundercloud. It can bring on torrential downpours instantly.

Name: Key Mace #2
Description: A small doll that can seal the goodness in the hearts of people. It does so to change them into minions of evil.

Name: Tenderness
Description: An adorable fairy that blesses lovers for eternal bliss. It is distinguished by a small heart on its head.

Name: Penguin Soldier
