Description: A low-level soldier among penguins that is armed with a sword. It attacks en masse with its comrades.

Name: Fairy Dragon
Description: A diminutive and extremely pretty dragon with dainty wings. Among the fairies, it is surprisingly strong.

Name: Obese Marmot of Nefariousness
Description: A fat, blue rodent with a horn that will gnaw on anything. It is ill-mannered in the extreme.

Name: Liquid Beast
Description: A liquid life form with no features save for its eyes. It can dissolve and move freely through water.

Name: Twin Long Rods #2
Description: An aquatic creature that has a pair of long, whiplike tails. It flails at opponents with its tails to attack.

Name: Great Bill
Description: A gigantic ducklike beast with a furry hide and a big beak. Its great big beak can swallow anything whole.

Name: Shining Friendship
Description: An angelic fairy that is dedicated to promoting friendship. She brings reconciliation to duelists who have become angry.

Name: Bladefly
Description: A red-and-black striped insect with swordlike forelegs. It flies at foes with its forelegs out.

Name: Electric Lizard
Description: A small lizard that uses electric power to stun its foe. It can stop one foe on the field from moving for one turn.

Name: Hiro's Shadow Scout
Description: A cyclopean fiend that serves a high-class fiend as a familiar. Its master employs it to scout the surroundings.

Name: Lady of Faith
Description: A devout young woman who has a restorative power. Her strange chanting can restore LP by 500.

Name: Twin-Headed Thunder Dragon
Description: A Thunder Dragon that has grown an additional head. It looses devastating thunderbolts to attack.

Name: Hunter Spider
Description: A voracious spider that hunts prey by spinning webs as traps. It devours anything that is caught in its webs.

Name: Armored Starfish
Description: A greenish starfish with a tough and durable body surface. The stiff body gives it relatively high defense.

Name: Hourglass of Courage
Description: A kindly fairy that is in the form of an hourglass with wings. It gives one courage when one is feeling down.

Name: Marine Beast
Description: A beastly being of the high seas with needle-sharp fangs. If it buries its fangs in its foe, it will not let go.

Name: Warrior of Tradition
Description: A female warrior who is drenched in the blood of her victims. She wanders battlefields, having lost the chance to die.

Name: Rock Spirit
Description: A fairy of boulders that looks like an earthenware statue. It is quite strong in terms of both attack and defense.

Name: Snakeyashi
Description: What appears to be a single creature is actually many snakes. When foes draw near, the snakes break rank to swarm.

Name: Succubus Knight
Description: A multi-armed magician who is skilled at casting dark spells. With her dark powers, she slaughters all opponents.

Name: Ill Witch
Description: A bedraggled girl who has the power to control the winds. She whips up sudden gusts that can blow everything away.

Name: The Thing That Hides in the Mud
Description: A goopy mess of a creature that lurks in dirt and mud unnoticed. If the ground appears to melt, this monster will emerge.

Name: High Tide Gyojin
Description: A humanoid warrior of the seas that is an expert swimmer. It has high attack power, relatively.

Name: Fairy of the Fountain
Description: A fairy with blue skin and hair who protects a sacred spring. She attacks anyone who spoils the spring without mercy.

Name: Amazon of the Seas
Description: A blue-haired mermaid who serves a deity of the seven seas. She watches guard over a an area of sanctity.

Name: Nekogal #2
Description: A felinelike beast warrior that deftly sidesteps attacks. She strikes with her sharp and hooked claws.

Name: Witch's Apprentice
Description: A starting witch with the ability to power up shadow-type monsters and power down light types on the own field.

Name: Armored Rat
Description: A seemingly shell-wearing rat with hair that is like an armor. Its tough hide provides a good deal of protection.

Name: Ancient Lizard Warrior
Description: A lizard warrior that appears as it did since the olden days. Surprisingly enough, it is stronger than it looks.

Name: Maiden of the Moonlight
Description: A magic-using maiden who is under the moon's protection. Her ethereal spells enchant foes into seeing illusions.

Name: Stone Ogre Grotto
Description: A gargantuan being that is composed of huge boulders and stones. The boulders are densely packed on its body.

Name: Winged Egg of New Life
Description: A delicately winged fairy that emerges from a curious egg. It is said to tell women that they have conceived a child.

Name: Night Lizard
Description: A lizard-man warrior that has been made a protector of the sea. It is easily recognized by its green scales.

Name: Queen's Double
Description: A female warrior who serves as a stand-in for her queen. She is not very useful, apparently.

Name: Blue-Winged Crown
Description: A bird that is engulfed in flames, giving it a bluish white color. It has a tuft of hair that looks like a crown.

Name: Trent
Description: A massive, ancient tree that guards a forest of fairies. It can turn the field into a forest.

Name: Queen of Autumn Leaves
Description: The Queen of the Emerald Forest and wife of the Spirit King. She lives among leaves in the vivid colors of autumn.

Name: Amphibious Bugroth
Description: A Terra Bugroth that has undergone major retrofitting. It is now capable of use in water as well as on land.

Name: Acid Crawler
Description: A gigantic insect larva that spits an extremely vile acid. The powerful acid melts everything.

Name: Invader of the Throne
Description: A devious, power-hungry woman who is unsatisfied as a queen. She hungers for the throne in the absence of the king.

Name: Mystical Sheep #1
Description: A long-tailed sheep with a fleece as dark as its heart. It employs illusory ruses and tricks.

Name: Disk Magician
Description: A machine that seals itself inside a mechanical disk. The only time it shows its identity is while it is attacking.

Name: Flame Viper
Description: A large-headed viper that exhales a roiling mass of flames. It moves with slippery quickness.

Name: Royal Guard
Description: A mechanized soldier that was developed to protect royalty. It has been endowed with the ability to think.

Name: Gruesome Goo
Description: An oozing mess of a monster, and a boss among the slime. While is may look the same as others, it is much more powerful.

Name: Hyosube
Description: A skinny, amphibious being, and a boss among the kappa clan. It is relatively strong for attacking, but has low defense.

Name: Machine Attacker
Description: A machine that was made to undertake suicidal ram attacks. It plows over foes by charging recklessly.

Name: Hibikime
Description: A warrior who emits a horrible noise that echoes harshly. The racket distracts foes into a standstill.

Name: Whiptail Crow
Description: A gargoylelike creature that has a long, whiplike tail. It strikes from above with its tail.

Name: Performance of Sword
Description: A dancing warrior girl with a sense of grace and beauty. She spins with flowing elegance.

Name: Hungry Burger
Description: A being that has assumed the guise of a mouth-watering burger. It wafts a tasty aroma to attract foes, then eats them.

Name: Sengenjin
Description: A primitive humanoid that possesses a Millennium Item. It relies on strength and nothing else, no matter what.

Name: Skull Guardian
Description: A humanoid being that has wicked swords in the place of arms. It upholds the rules, and forbids all cheating.

Name: Tri-Horned Dragon
Description: A divine dragon of enormous power belied by its appearance. It is distinguished by the three horns on its head.

Name: Serpent Night Dragon
Description: A serpentine dragon that emerged from a heart of darkness. It is the embodiment of the darkness in a wicked knight.

Name: Skull Knight
Description: A warrior magician who conducts many rituals in the dark world. He is adept at fighting with weapons and spells.

Name: Cosmo Queen
Description: A woman of distinguished demeanor and enormous power. She is said to rule over all the stars and planets in the cosmos.

Name: Chakra
Description: A bizarre fiend that has the ability to alter its body shape. While it shifts shape, it strikes with tentaclelike arms.

Name: Crab Turtle
Description: A powerful turtle from whose shell protrudes crab pincers. It is very strong in terms of both ATK and DEF.

Name: Mikazukinoyaiba
Description: A ferocious dragon warrior armed with a crescent-blade sword. It is said to have come from the moon.

Name: Meteor Dragon
Description: A dragon that came from the outer reaches of space. It fell to earth with meteors.

Name: Meteor B. Dragon
Description: A dragon whose body is a meteor that roils in red-black fire. Its body heat vaporizes everything nearby.

Name: Firewing Pegasus
Description: A horse with massive wings that blaze in vivid, scarlet flames. It is a fiery sight to behold as it gallops across the sky.

Name: Psycho-Puppet
Description: A malevolent puppet that performs odd, debilitating dances. Its dancing inflicts pain on those that see it.

Name: Garma Sword
Description: A swordsman that attacks with a furious flurry of six swords. It hacks apart everything within reach.

Name: Javelin Beetle
Description: A hardy beetle that is both strong on attack and defense. If it traps a foe with its pincers, the enemy is cut in half.

Name: Fortress Whale
Description: A whale with a massive cannon mounted in a turret on its back. It hides in the sea and sinks foes with the gun.

Name: Dokurorider
Description: A solitary ghoul that rides a motorcycle with a skull. It rides through wastelands in a cloud of dust.

Name: Mask of Shine & Dark
Description: A sinister mask that uses illusions to confuse its foes. It creates a swirling vision of dark and light.

Name: Magician of Black Chaos
Description: A master of magicians who embodies the sinister power of chaos. He is the fusion of shadow and light.

Name: Slot Machine
Description: A robot with limbs coming out of its slot machine body. Its abilities are said to change with the scores on the slots.

Name: Space Megatron
Description: A robot that is constructed primarily with sets of semicircles. It attacks with lasers mounted at its sides and the center.

Name: Red Archery Girl
Description: A mermaid archer who conceals herself in a clam shell. She can weaken a foe monster, and immobilize it next turn.

Name: Ryu-Ran
Description: A vicious dragon that wears an egg shell as if for shelter. Beware - mistaking this dragon for an infant may be disastrous.

Name: Manga Ryu-Ran
Description: A cartoony dragon that wears an egg shell for protection. Despite its whimsical appearance, it is very strong.

Name: Toon Mermaid
Description: A cartoony mermaid with a bow inside a giant clam shell. It is a Red Archery Girl that has been transformed by Toon World.

Name: Toon Summoned Skull
Description: A cartoony skeleton fiend that has been summoned from its castle. It is a Summoned Skull in the Toon World.

Name: Dark-Eyes Illusionist
Description: A pathetic being with an ATK and DEF rating of 0 for both. It is needed as a tribute for summoning Relinquished.

Name: Relinquished
Description: A horrifying monster that has single malevolent eye. It can steal the abilities of a monster on the foe's field.

Name: Jigen Bakudan
Description: An animated time bomb that can get around on its own accord. Its blast force is said to affect the monsters on its side.

Name: Thousand-Eyes Idol
Description: A strange, enchanted idol that has eyes all over its body. It glares at foes to stop them in their tracks.

Name: Thousand-Eyes Restrict
Description: A monster with countless eyes. It can steal the abilities of a monster on the foe's field to power up two levels.

Name: Steel Ogre Grotto #2
Description: A mechanical golem of an extremely sturdy, rugged build. Its metallic arms are very thick.

Name: Blast Sphere
Description: A mechanized bomb that has hooks used for latching onto its enemy. It defeats its for with a devastating explosion.

Name: Hyozanryu
Description: A horned dragon whose entire body is composed of diamonds. It looses dazzling flashes that blind its foes.

Name: Alpha The Magnet Warrior
Description: A magnetized monster that can meld with Beta and Gamma into one. The other two must be on the field to integrate with Alpha.

Name: Legion the Fiend Jester
Description: A magician on the dark side in the guise of a jester. It bobs and weaves to avoid attack, then strikes sharply.

Name: Invitation to a Dark Sleep
Description: A masked magician that summons black, sleep-inducing clouds. It can make all monsters on the foe's field fall asleep.

Name: Lord of D.
Description: A monstrous magician that wears a large, concealing cape. It has the power to rule over many of the dragons.

Name: Red-Eyes Black Metal Dragon
Description: A Red-Eyes Black Dragon that has been metalized for more power. Its type has changed from dragon to machine.

Name: Barrel Dragon
Description: A mechanical dragon fitted with cannons. It can wipe out up to 3 monsters on the opponent's field with a 2-in-1 success rate.

Name: Hannibal Necromancer
Description: A sinister creature that revels in the dark arts of necromancy. It is formed from the souls of ghouls.

Name: Panther Warrior
Description: A feline warrior that attacks faster than sweeping winds. Its speed easily tops 60mph.

Name: Three-Headed Geedo
Description: A dark fiend that supports three heads on its skinny frame. Its heads are said to grow back if they are to be cut off.

Name: Gazelle the King of Mythical Beasts
Description: A horned lion beast that reigns over mythical beasts. It is said to have over 10,000 beasts under its command.

Name: Stone Statue of the Aztecs
Description: A monumental statue made in ancient times by a long lost culture. Tens of thousands of sacrifices were made on it.

Name: Berfomet
Description: An immense being with huge wings that keep it aloft. The wings are said to be able to repel any wind.

Name: Chimera the Flying Mythical Beast
Description: A beast that obtained enormous power by achieving fusion. However, its life lasts a mere five minutes.

Name: Gear Golem the Moving Fortress
Description: A mechanized fortress that features both mobility and defense. It is made of enchanted stones.

Name: Jinzo
Description: An android of great power distinguished by its thick, long neck. It can destroy all the trap cards on the opponent's field.

Name: Swordsman of Landstar
Description: A delicate fairy swordsman that is yet unskilled in combat. It makes up for its weak sword skills with mystical abilities.

Name: Cyber Raider
Description: A helmeted and muscular brute whose identity is a secret. He was a villain who perpetrated evil deeds in cyber space.

Name: The Fiend Megacyber
Description: A creature that resulted from a fusion of electronics and magic. The fusion process made it powerful.

Name: Reflect Bounder
Description: A magical mirror being that can take the ATK power of a monster on the foe's field to cause LP loss in return for its own life.

Name: Beta The Magnet Warrior
Description: A magnetized monster that fuses with Alpha and Gamma into one. The other two must be on the field to integrate with Beta.

Name: Big Shield Gardna
Description: A legendary shield of a massive size and ornate design. It is said to have fended off a million-strong army in the past.

Name: Doll of Demise
Description: A fiendish doll that was once beloved, but discarded later. It came to life to exact revenge for abandonment.

Name: Dark Magician Girl
Description: A beautiful female counterpart to the male Dark Magician. She powers up if there is a Dark Magician in the graveyard.

Name: Alligator's Sword
Description: A lizardman that is highly skilled in the handling of swords. It swings its sword at the speed of sound.

Name: Insect Queen
Description: A powerful creature that rules over the insects. It can be powered up based on the number of insects on the own field.

Name: Parasite Paracide
Description: A parasitic insect that obtains food from the hapless host. It has the power to latch onto a monster on the foe's field.

Name: Skull-Mark Lady Bug
Description: A ladybug that has a skull-and-crossbones on its back. In return for its own demise, it can restore LP by 500.

Name: Tiny Guardian
Description: A diminutive warrior who peers out from beneath its cap. Its sharp vision catches every movement made by its foes.

Name: Pinch Hopper
Description: A grasshopperlike insect that can sacrifice itself. For its own demise, it can summon an insect from the own hand

Name: Blue-Eyes Toon Dragon
Description: A cartoony dragon that was a Blue-Eyes White Dragon. It had been drawn into the Toon World and transformed.

Name: The Unhappy Maiden
Description: A pitiable young girl who is dressed in tattered old rags. She ekes out her living by peddling wares in a town on a daily basis.

Name: Wall of Illusion
Description: An enchanted wall that shows illusory visions to its foes. It befuddles foes into making their attacks go astray.

Name: Neo the Magic Swordsman
Description: A swordsman who is equally adept at both swordplay and sorcery. He is useful to have around as a comrade.

Name: Man-Eating Treasure Chest
Description: A fiendish treasure chest that savors people with valuables. It chomps down on anyone that ventures too close.

Name: Sorcerer of the Doomed
Description: A ghoulish sorcerer that is skilled in the art of necromancy. It has struck a contract with darkness.

Name: Sword Hunter
Description: A solitary warrior on a quest for the world's famous swords. His search leads him all over the world.

Name: Drill Bug
Description: A wormlike insect that burrows inside its foe's body to eat. It is a dangerous monster that drains the prey from within.

Name: Deepsea Warrior
Description: An undersea warrior in a wet suit made for deep water fighting. The suit can withstand high pressure of 10,000 bar.

Name: Bite Shoes
Description: A devious monster that has assumed the guise of a boot. If anyone were to put it on, it would bite off his foot.

Name: Spikebot
Description: A mechanical monster that wields a steel ball weighing a ton. However, its accuracy isn't very good.

Name: Beast of Gilfer
Description: A peculiar, dragonlike fiend. In return for its own demise, it can power down all monsters on the foe's field.

Name: The Portrait's Secret
Description: A portrait painting that has a sinister reputation of bad luck. It is said to bring misfortune to all those who own it.

Name: The Gross Ghost of Fled Dreams
Description: A dark fiend that haunts the dreams of those it comes to possess. Once it is in control, the victim cannot awaken voluntarily.

Name: Gate Sword
Description: A dark warrior that has assumed the guise of a caped sword. It cleaves everything it touches in half.

Name: Steel Fan Fighter
Description: A warrior who uses a steel fan that is etched with a dragon. He battles as if he were dancing.

Name: Leopard Girl
Description: A beast warrior that breathes on the neck of its foe. The startled foe is then shredded by this quick being.

Name: The Last Warrior from Another Planet
Description: An armored warrior that won't quit his fight to guard his planet. However, he is the last being alive in his world.

Name: Dunames Dark Witch
Description: A courageous fairy of light that has a strong sense of justice. She will not run from any battle against the forces of darkness.

Name: Garnecia Elefantis
Description: An immense elephant being that boasts terrifying strength. Fissures appear with every step it takes.

Name: Total Defense Shogun
Description: A brave general who fought to protect his loved ones. He endured an assault that raged for a thousand days.

Name: Beast of Talwar
Description: A fiend that bears a weapon that is highly exclusive for use. Even among fiends, only the swordplay experts may touch it.

Name: Cyber-Tech Alligator
Description: A winged dragon that has been made powerful using technology. It was made a cyborg by its owner on its deathbed.

Name: Talons of Shurilane
Description: An illusory fiend that hides itself in mysterious mirages. Those that see it are ripped apart by its sharp claws.

Name: The Stern Mystic
Description: A wise old magician whose stern demeanor reflect his high morals. Before him, no lie can go unnoticed.

Name: Baron of the Fiend Sword
Description: A noble who brandishes a sword imbued with dark emotions. He chases down quarry with grim and relentless purpose.

Name: Shining Abyss
Description: A peculiar winged being that embodies two opposing attributes. It has both the power of light and darkness.

Name: Headless Knight
Description: A knight who had been beheaded on a fake charge of treason. Now its fiendish specter wanders without a head.

Name: Soldier Ari
Description: An ant that turned vicious as a result of spontaneous mutation. Its body is relatively stiff and durable.

Name: Gearfried the Iron Knight
Description: A warrior that has been constructed out of tensile steel. Its steel hands have sharp cutting edges.

Name: Humanoid Slime
Description: A watery, gel-like being that has taken the shape of a human. It was made by infusing a slime with human genetic material.

Name: Worm Drake
Description: A wormlike creature that uses its long body to entrap foes. There is no escape from its binding grip.

Name: Humanoid Worm Drake
Description: A gelatinous creature that was created from a fusion between a Humanoid Slime and a Worm Drake.

Name: Revival Jam
Description: A being that multiplies by splitting into two identical halves. If there is room on the player's field it can split into two.

Name: Buster Blader
Description: A warrior that can be powered up based on the number of dragons on the opponent's field.

Name: Dark Necrofear
Description: A being that can take over a monster on the opponent's field. The affected monster is put under the player's control.

Name: Cyber Jar
Description: A pod-type robot of a jarlike design from a future world. It carries a powerful bomb inside its body.

Name: Banisher of the Light
Description: A forbidding figure that has been made the guardian of light. He has been commanded to banish those who serve the dark side.

Name: Giant Rat
Description: A powerful rat that has grown to an abnormally big size. Exposure to radiation is thought to be the cause.

Name: Senju of the Thousand Hands
Description: An imposing fairy that has numerous arms for attacking in droves. The flailing of its forest of arms causes major damage.

Name: UFO Turtle
Description: A gigantic turtle that has made its shell from a UFO. Amazingly enough, it is said to be able to fly.

Name: Flash Assailant
Description: An extremely quick fiend that uses its speed to best advantage. If it is seen, the witness is sure to be killed instantly.

Name: Karate Man
Description: A lean and buff karate master with fists of steel. He has the power to shatter 10,000 roof tiles.

Name: Dark Zebra
Description: A sinister zebra that has a unicornlike horn on its forehead. It befuddles foes by making its stripes move around quickly.

Name: Giant Germ
Description: A terrifying germ that has an extremely high level of toxicity. Even one of these germs is said to defeat even a dragon.

Name: Nimble Momonga
Description: A flying squirrel that flies around its foe, out of reach. When it sees a chance, it goes for the foe's throat with fangs.

Name: Spear Cretin
Description: A impish fiend that roams about in the darkness aimlessly. If it spots prey, it goes on the attack with its spear in hand.

Name: Shining Angel
Description: An ethereal fairy that shoots a beam from the halo on it head. The beam stops foes in their tracks.

Name: Boar Soldier
Description: A porcine beast warrior that wields a massive stone axe. It destroys everything that happens to be within sight.

Name: Mother Grizzly
Description: A bruin that tears at the foe's throat with hooked claws. The foe's life is over in just five seconds.

Name: Flying Kamakiri #1
Description: A dragonflylike insect that breathes intense flames to strike. If it spots prey, it flies above it and spits fire immediately.

Name: Ceremonial Bell
Description: A gleaming bell that is used to mark celebratory occasions. Its pealing brings solace to those that hear it.

Name: Sonic Bird
Description: A goggled bird monster with jet units slung over its back. It is a supersonic monster that travels faster than sound.

Name: Mystic Tomato
Description: A monster that had been a man who died by choking on tomatoes. His anger at his murder made him this monster.

Name: Kotodama
Description: A freaky fairy whose body is scored with peculiar red lines. Hearing its voice results in ten days of agony, then death.

Name: Obelisk the Tormentor
Description: A monster that can wipe out all monsters on the foe's field. At the same time, it hits the foe with 4,000LP worth of damage.

Name: Slifer the Sky Dragon
Description: A dragon that can power up based on the cards in the hand. For every card in the player's hand, power is upped 3 levels.

Name: The Winged Dragon of Ra
Description: A dragon that has the power to cut its LP to 1 and hit the opponent with the LP amount that it has lost.

Name: Flying Fish
Description: A fish that is said to bring luck to those who see it flying. The lucky witnesses are said to have three wishes come true.

Name: Amphibian Beast
Description: A creature that attacks quickly like a beast while on land. In water, it strikes fast like a fish.

Name: Alligator's Sword Dragon
Description: A lizardman with a dragon steed created from the fusion of a Baby Dragon and an Alligator's Sword.

Name: Rocket Warrior
Description: A smaller warrior that can transform into a speedy rocket. It can power down a chosen monster on the opponent's field.

Name: Aqua Serpent
Description: An aquatic serpent that crawls along the bottom of the sea. It suddenly appears and attacks when it spots prey.

Name: The Legendary Fisherman
Description: A whale-riding man of the sea with a compassionate spirit. He cannot be bested by anyone when battling at sea.

Name: Morphing Jar #2
Description: A jar that was constructed in the world of fiends. Anything placed inside it can never be recovered.

Name: Vorse Raider
Description: A ferocious beast warrior that dedicates itself to evil deeds. It finds joy in carrying out its misdeeds.

Name: Flame Champion
Description: A swordsman equipped with a large shield that is awash in flames. The fiery shield negates any kind of attack.

Name: Twin-Headed Fire Dragon
Description: A fiery winged dragon with two heads and a tail with talons. It is said to have been formed at the creation of the universe

Name: Darkfire Soldier #1
Description: A covert operations specialist who is cloaked in flames. He is an expert in the handling of explosives.

Name: Mr. Volcano
Description: A gentleman who is skilled in the exotic art of pyrotechnics. While he is mild-mannered, he has a terrible temper.

Name: Darkfire Soldier #2
Description: A swordsman burning bright with both his swords at the ready. He gained the ability to don fire when he fell into a volcano.

Name: Kiseitai
Description: A parasitic, wormlike fiend that affects the actions of its host. If you do something you know to be wrong, this is to blame.

Name: Cyber Falcon
Description: A mechanized falcon that is equipped with a powerful jet engine. It can fly at the speed of sound.

Name: Gamma The Magnet Warrior
Description: A magnetized monster that can meld with Alpha and Beta into one. The other two must be on the field to integrate with Gamma.

Name: Flying Kamakiri #2
Description: An overgrown praying mantis that is able to take to the skies. It loves to eat other insects.

Name: Harpie's Brother
Description: A winged humanoid being who is able to fly at Mach 5 speed. His eyes glint with a light sharper than a hawk's.

Name: Grand Tiki Elder
Description: A masked fiend that uses freaky incantations to attack. Its chanted curses cause foes to drop as if stricken physically.

Name: The Masked Beast
Description: A masked fiend with the torso of a human and a staff. It has learned the world's most horrifying spell.

Name: The Earl of Demise
Description: A fiend of aristocratic status and fearsome bearing. He is feared by not only humans, but also by weaker fiends.

Name: Boneheimer
Description: A sea horse that wanders with the waves in search of prey. It feeds by draining the prey of all body fluids.

Name: Flame Dancer
Description: A fiery creature that swings a rope of fire as it approaches. Don't make the mistake of catching this creature's one eye.

Name: Zombyra the Dark
Description: A superhero on the dark side. In return for for powering down, he can destroy one monster on the foe's field.

Name: Earthbound Spirit
Description: A fiendish spirit that cannot take leave from earth. It is made from the souls of soldiers vanquished in battle.

Name: Embodiment of Apophis
Description: A giant that is the living embodiment of an enormous snake. The snake is described in Egyptian myths as the ruler of darkness.

Name: Ancient Lamp
Description: An animated magic lamp. It can summon a La Jinn the Mystical Genie of the Lamp if there is open space on the own field.

Name: Amazon Chain Master
Description: A combative female warrior who is skilled at using a chain. She lives in northern outlands where she hunts for pleasure.

Name: Thunder Nyan Nyan
Description: A clumsy elemental infant who lives on the tops of clouds. She often falls, causing lightning to crash down each time.

Name: Injection Fairy Lily
Description: A delicate fairy that bears a large syringe as her weapon. If angered, she shoots needles from the syringe endlessly.

Name: Dark Magician
Description: A slender magician who is among the best of all his kind. His attack and defense stats are top class.

Name: Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon
Description: The ultimate of all dragons that has three awe-inspiring heads. It is formed by three Blue-Eyes White Dragons.

Name: Executor - Makyura
Description: A menacing monster that has been given the role of an executioner. It slices up the condemned with the sharp claws on its forelegs.

Name: Viser Des
Description: A torture monster that use a vise as its weapon of choice. It flies at its target's head, then tightens the vise.

Name: Amazon Sword Woman
Description: A female warrior who is an expert at battling with a sword. She easily wields a heavy sword in one hand.

Name: Des Volstgalph
Description: A dragon that can wipe out a monster on the foe's field. At the same time, it hits the foe with 500LP worth of damage.

Name: Toon Dark Magician Girl
Description: A cartoony female counterpart to the male Dark Magician. She powers up if there is a Dark Magician in the graveyard.

Name: Gilford the Lightning
Description: A warrior of great strength with a devastating power. He can wipe out all monsters on the foe's field.

Name: Mystical Beast Serket
Description: A powerful scorpionlike being that can envelop a monster on the foe's field to power itself up.

Name: Cyber Harpie
Description: A Harpie Lady who has been modified. She has the ability to power up Harpie's Pet Dragons on the player's field.

Name: Lightning Conger
Description: A massive eel that uses lightning to destroy its foes. It is said to have evolved from an electric eel.

Name: Exarion Universe
Description: A centaurlike being that has the power to hit the opponent with LP loss identical to its ATK. It then powers down.

Name: Legendary Fiend
Description: A fiend with large black wings that is described in legends. It has the ability to power itself up.

Name: Gadget Soldier
Description: A mechanical soldier that was produced to serve as a weapon. It is made of a rustproof metal.

Name: Melchid the Four-Face Beast
Description: A strange monster that switches its four masks in battle. By switching masks, it changes its attack modes four ways.

Name: Nuvia the Wicked
Description: A dark fiend that had once been a woman fixated on revenge. She changed to this form by selling her soul to a dark entity.

Name: Masked Beast Des Gardius
Description: A fiendish masked monster that makes prey of human beings. The mask is said to show the faces of the people it has eaten.

Name: Valkyrion the Magna Warrior
Description: A magnetized warrior that can separate into Alpha, Beta, and Gamma if there are two or more open spaces on the own field.

Name: Red-Eyes Black Metal Dragon
Description: A ferocious mechanized dragon that boasts great strength. It is a Red-Eyes Black Dragon that was metalized for power.

Name: Red-Eyes B. Dragon
Description: A sinister black dragon with eyes that shine a deep scarlet. It furiously spouts black flames that incinerate all things.

Name: Spherous Lady
Description: A vampiric woman who uses her beauty to lure careless victims. She bites the necks of prey and sucks it dry of all blood.

Name: Blue-Eyes White Dragon
Description: A legendary dragon that takes pride in its enormous power. Its powers of destruction far exceed comprehension.

Name: Dark Sage
Description: An imposing and powerful sage that dons striking black clothes. He is a Dark Magician who gained power over many years.

Name: F.G.D.
Description: A gargantuan dragon with five heads that is simply invincible. It is formed by the fusion of five strong dragons.

Name: Master of Dragon Soldier
Description: A huge and awesomely strong dragon that can be powered up based on the number of dragons on the player's field.
